msgid ""
"Defeat the nearby enemy. To attack a building, click on its doors, choose "
"the\n"
"number of attacking soldiers, then send them via the attack button."
msgstr ""
"Derrota al enemigo mas cercano. Para atacar un edificio, haz click en las "
"puertas,\n"
"selecciona el numero de soldados para atacar y luego envíalos a través del "
"botón\n"
"de atacar."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:673
