#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:628
msgid ""
"Defense is the value that is subtracted from the attack value. The "
"barbarians\n"
"can not train in this skill and therefore have always defense level 0 which\n"
"means that they always get 3 hitpoints subtracted from the damage inflicted. "
"If\n"
"an attacker with an attack value of 15 hitpoints hits a barbarian soldier, "
"the\n"
"barbarian would lose 15 - 3 = 12 hitpoints. The 3 hitpoints that are "
"subtracted\n"
"are because of the defense ability."
msgstr ""
"Defensa es el valor que es restado del valor de ataque. Los bárbaros\n"
"no pueden entrenar esta habilidad y por lo tanto siempre tienen defensa "
"nivel 0, \n"
"lo que significa que siempre se les resta 3 puntos de vida del daño "
"recibido. Si\n"
"un atacante con un valor de ataque de 15 puntos de vida golpea a un soldado "
"bárbaro, el\n"
"bárbaro perdería 15 - 3 = 12 puntos de vida. Los 3 puntos de vida que son "
"restados\n"
"son por la habilidad de defensa."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:627
msgid "Defense:"
msgstr "Defensa:"

